Package org.usfirst.frc.team3494.robot.commands.auto

Package of all autonomous command sequences and commands for use in autonomous only.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AngleTurn
    Turns the robot using the gyro board mounted to the RoboRIO.
    ConstructedAuto
    Creates an auto program from a passed-in list of commands.
    DistanceDrive
    Drives a given distance.
    DropGear
    Drops the gear on the peg if the linebrak sensor is tripped.
    NullAuto
    an auto program that does nothing
    PegDrive  
    PIDAngleDrive
    Turns the robot to an angle using PID.
    PIDFullDrive
    Drives straight/forward with an angle (WIP) using the drivetrain's PID loop.
    SetGearGrasp  
    XYDrive
    Drives to a point relative to the robot.
